<p>&#8230; As a young spawn, I was told tales of such&#8230; <em>greatness</em>. It seemed unfathomable then, only a remnant of the past universes; the ones to outshine us. They were the universes of kings and legends. But, I digress. <em>This</em> is why I was born&#8230; to see PesterBot and Gargantua The Dinosaur have a petty argument.</p>
<p>+1, my generous traveler.</p>

